node.text:
We are excited to introduce our Brewing for Diversity Scholarship initiative in partnership with @ucsdextension and their brewing program! Ballast Point will grant one scholarship per year, and recipients will be selected by partner team members and the @sdbrewers Guild Inclusion Committee. We can’t wait to support YOU and a more inclusive brewing community. 

Visit the link in our bio for more information on how to apply!

node.text:
Did you know that Calico was the very first beer brewed on the original 15-barrel brewhouse at Home Brew Mart?

Since then it has seen a name and artwork change but this Amber Ale is rooted in history 🙌🏽

node.text:
The wait is over 🍻👏🏽 

In our next installment of the BeerX podcast series, we chat with some awesome local breweries. We sit down with Latchkey, Eppig, Westbrew, and Karl Strauss to talk about our favorite subject: BEER. 

Listen in as we cheers to good beers! 🍻

Missed the first installment? BeerX: The Bands is available for listening now. Link in bio 🎶
